  "texts": [
    "Its sampler, based on the NSGA-II algorithm, provides a fast approach to multi-objective optimization.",
    "Furthermore, Optuna introduces a pruning strategy that terminates unpromising trials prematurely, accelerating the optimization process [114].",
    "This combination of mechanisms is essential for high-performance optimization under constrained resources.• Versatile Architecture: Optuna's design caters to a wide range of experimental needs, from lightweight experiments on interactive interfaces to scalable distributed computing tasks.",
    "This versatility is critical for adapting to different computational environments and scales, making Optuna a powerful tool for optimizing ML models [114].• Real-world Applications and Community Support: Optuna's effectiveness in real-world applications, from deep learning models to system configuration optimization, further validates its capabilities.",
    "Its open-source nature and active community support enhance its adaptability and reliability, ensuring that Optuna remains at the forefront of optimization technology [114].Given these features, Optuna was selected as the framework for our case study."
